title: Hoover WindTunnel 3 Upright Vacuum Turbo Tool Not Picking Up
description: Hi Buyer Of Stuff: We saw your review on Amazon. We had a few tips to help you use your Turbo Tool more efficiently. The vacuum in our video is a different color than yours, but it is otherwise the same. Let us know if you need any more help! -Felicia
